titles.title: Expressing the condolences of the House on the death of the Honorable Frank Tejeda.

action.text: DEBATE - The House proceeded with one hour of debate.
The previous question was ordered without objection.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: 2/4/1997--Introduced. Expresses the condolences of the House of Representatives on the death of the Honorable Frank Tejeda, a Representative from the State of Texas.
